Clinical Decision Support Questionnaire Structure

1. Biological Sex --> Sex
2. Age at diagnosis --> Diangosis Age
3. Primary tumor site --> CANCER_TYPE
4. Anatomic subsite --> Tumor Disease Anatomic Site
5. Specimen collection type --> Sample Type
6. Pathologic Staging (AJCC) --> Neoplasm Disease Stage American Joint Committee on Cancer Code
7. T (Primary Tumor Extension) --> American Joint Committee on Cancer Tumor Stage Code
8. N (Regional Lymph Nodes) -->  American Joint Committee on Cancer Code
9. M (Distant Metastasis) --> American Joint Committee on Cancer Metastasis Stage Code
10. Molecular Histologic Subtype --> Subtype
11. Genomic Instability Metrics:
    - MSI Score --> MSIsensor Score
    - Tumor Mutational Burden --> TMB (nonsynonymus)

